Example Usage
python
from data_generator.generate_orders import generate_all_batches

generate_all_batches(
    n_batches=6,
    n_records_per_batch=1000,
    output_dir="data/orders"
)
This will produce:

Code
data/orders/
    orders_batch_1.csv
    orders_batch_2.csv
    ...
    orders_batch_6.csv
Each file contains schema drift, nulls, invalid values, and duplicates.

